              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5103869597629597785">When Daisy Mason disappears during a family party, literally everyone seems like a suspect. But who is really responsible and what really happened to her? This was an intense, well-paced psychological thriller, with lots of red herrings, family drama and backstory, interesting side plots, and twists and turns all the way up until the last page. I will definitely be checking out more in this series! <br/><br/>Please excuse typos/name misspellings. Entered on screen reader.<br/></span>

